== Magic Overview ==

Magic is divided into three categories, each with its own charge pool. Each spell costs '''1 charge''' from its respective pool.

{| class="wikitable"
! Category !! Charge Type !! Spells !! Notes
|-
| White Magic || White charges || Cure, Heal, Life, Exit || Healing/Support
|-
| Black Magic || Black charges || Fire, Ice, Thunder, Quake || Offensive elements
|-
| Wizard Magic || Wizard charges || Blizzard, Meteor, White, Flare || Advanced/powerful
|}

'''Note:''' All spells cost exactly 1 charge of their type. There are no variable MP costs.

